methods.name: go
methods.comment:
Will attempt to navigate to the location as appropriate.  For example, it may use the goto service
 to navigate the code browser to a progam and and address.  Or it could launch a browser and
 display a web page.

params.name: provider
params.comment:
a service provider that this location can use to find a service to help with
 navigation.

return.comment: true if the navigation was successful, false otherwise.
